18#include "ResultPoint.h"
19#include <cmath>
20
21namespace ZXing {
22
23float ResultPoint::Distance(int aX, int aY, int bX, int bY)
24{
25 auto dx = static_cast<float>(aX - bX);
26 auto dy = static_cast<float>(aY - bY);
27 return std::sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
28}
29
30} // ZXing
